As the current generation comes to a close, gamers are getting a chance to play some killer games that push the limits of what is possible with the current tech. These games have offered plenty exemplary experiences and stories. However, none have been as fun as Saints Row 4. Not only does the gameplay offer the player a delightful play experience, the story is wonderfully absurd and full of some memorable character moments. Killing people with the power of dubstep and telekinesis is a special moment that Saints Row 4 offers the player, but is not content with simply giving them that type of destruction and keeps giving more. Despite whatever minor graphical flaws the game has, it is highly recommended. Gamers should play this; it is well worth their time.
